properties.Name: ServiceRequestChargeType
properties.Description:
A charge (fee) type that may be applied to a Service Request.

Ex:
- Application Fee
- Processing Charge
- Third-party Information Charge
- Additional Debit Card Charge
- Shipping Charge 
- Order Surcharge 
- Customs Charge 
- Return Charge 
- Administrative Charge 
- Re-stocking Charge
- Re-routing Charge

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestChargeTypeId

Columns.Description: The name of a Service Request Charge Type.

Columns.Name: ServiceRequestChargeTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of a Service Request Charge Type.
